Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫神饭看上去很好吃 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我试着用海里的食材做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你还能在这时候搞自创料理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫神拉面的新菜品对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 尼娜 你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是莱姆拉斯号和加利琉斯号 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们别太得意忘形啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发需要准将的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将回风花市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡 妳呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是要尽全力继续找真白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说现在的状况下 我也无法使用乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市内就由加尔德罗贝来对付 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡鲁教授
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长传来好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点事想跟加尔德罗贝的学园长谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追随古老传说的指引 终于来到这片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之谷却是连愕天王也无法跨越的暴风彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跨越它果然是痴人说梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统领
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统领
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说有真白传来的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们身处被暴风禁锢的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点来迎接我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来发生过那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不好意思 全被我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是相当饿了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡那家伙 有说过什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没有遇到艾莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…艾莉卡那家伙到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不懂我的苦心 光是长胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白没了艾莉卡就会感到寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 干脆尼娜你来当我的乙HiME吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我散歩去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡 为保护村子我们要先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡 气势不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 卡鲁教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找你了 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办 我又游不了多远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之谷真是不可思议的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫神大人教我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白殿下讨厌艾莉卡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人其实感情很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所以才会吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说她俩是女王和部下 倒不如说是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真好啊 乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽 帅气又强大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 得到力量其实是件很可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一失误 就会造成无可挽回的大错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 和这个是一样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神山…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神山在鸣叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏结界之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白和尼娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告各国情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔里斯 Delta乙HiME部队准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路提西亚 罗姆尔斯和雷姆斯国境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister罗拉 Meister卡拉准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜 Meister艾茵准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗林斯和卡尔蒂亚也做好了攻击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有Meister的国家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花由Meister莎拉 阿尔泰由Meister玛雅负责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都已抵达指定位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代理系统亦准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都能开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 如果展开攻击 奴兽复活的可能性非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样等下去 迟早会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如先下手为强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是各国首脑的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿真祖大人保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给萨拉和玛雅认证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代理系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我认证 命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物质化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到后山避难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真白陛下她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是无法给它致命一击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能赶在复活前打倒它就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨的小啰啰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖二三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到强烈的认证波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三大人的反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵了Server System
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到二三大人与各奴兽的连结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续吸收着高次元物质化能源
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是那家伙干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授 解除连接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 对方用Administrator账号锁住了系统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 各处的奴兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地的奴兽都开始复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾…艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白 认证
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍天的力量果然还未…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这样下去会没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和艾尔里斯时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴兽在自我修复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 没什么办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说我有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正伤脑筋呢吧 我倒是有个好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 是有条件的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我快说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这是我能办到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀 喜欢真白女王 也喜欢艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜 Meister舞衣 猫神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有猫和海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要守护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它收起来吧 由我来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决不会重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要缔结契约?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是海神之翠玉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这次 请让我当你的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已为我所犯的过错忏悔过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且对乙HiME感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是对力量本身感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想守护这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止了我和凪大公的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你和艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的想法是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩戴海神之翠玉的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名 将汝之力量释放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就乖乖待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗就请交给乙HiME吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物质化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是一样破绽百出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都看不下去了 所以就来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡 苍天的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡 你打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 不过你也要打我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我犯错了 你就再这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能手下留情的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予吾之乙HiME苍天的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到猫神山的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一位置还捕捉到GEM的高次元物质化反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及尤娜的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立即确认
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎绶之红玉--Meister舞衣正与奴兽交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有苍天之青玉Zwei艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是失落的GEM--海神之翠玉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落的GEM？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尼娜·王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡 尼娜 舞衣 听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经捕捉到你们的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 我方现在要开始实行某个作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也注意听好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴兽和尤娜的复活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为真祖大人在操控着它们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在会使用最后一支Core Cylinder
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断它们之间的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但时间只有120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须在这时间内打倒尤娜及所有奴兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 必须得办到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护这颗星球 以及它的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你还真敢赌啊 学院长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来关于我们的交涉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 等等 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始啰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动代理系统
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接至 Valkyrie回路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始连接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认证干涉系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒数开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做你该做的事 艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们与我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的意志若能相通…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候不能犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧 艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Master
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们动手吧 尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我俩的话 绝对没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和真白殿下果然是很相称的女王与乙HiME呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.33,0:23:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜呢 消灭它了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 各国的奴兽正逐渐毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.70,0:23:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Clear呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你们杀出了条生路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.51,0:23:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然花了不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所拨的电话由于某些原因无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能这样啊 夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:24:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你们了 这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 新的猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了抓它费了我不少功夫喔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.08,0:24:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是伽具土
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:24:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣 我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.69,0:24:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 真白呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.86,0:24:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.28,0:25:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惊人的光景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.07,0:25:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳正沿着星球升起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.76,0:25:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.18,0:25:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们与大家一起守护的星球喔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.77,0:25:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快看 看到了喔 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.83,0:25:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是风花市
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.77,0:25:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.87,0:25:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好美
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.09,0:25:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想让真白看看这风景
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是从这里俯瞰这世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.32,0:25:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.39,0:25:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪会这么粗枝大叶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.08,0:25:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.32,0:25:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡 我想更仔细地看看这星球
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.13,0:25:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我们居住的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.45,0:25:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着那太阳冲刺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.67,0:25:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Master
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.51,0:27:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要成为乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.75,0:27:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要当上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.70,0:28:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一场加尔德罗贝封印的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.69,0:28:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 便是先代的乙HiME觉醒之时
